Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計  我要你成為它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Buddy, I want you to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得肯定是誤會了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think there's been a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一名專業的演員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See, I am a professional actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才會在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need somebody who can be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅只是穿著服裝的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}more than just a guy in a suit.
