Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能賦予他生命的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who can bring him to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Without you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他什么都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都沒有量我的身材\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't take my measurements.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道穿著能合適\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you know it'd fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然能合適了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course it fits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這屬于你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How does it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們倆是天造地設啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seems like you two were made for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉過來讓我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see you move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, how do I move?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得要你在試鏡時做的動作嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember the thing you did in your audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你試試\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把胳膊舉起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raise your arms up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺成一個三角形\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together like a triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供奉的姿勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out like an offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺一個飛機的姿勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then you fly like a plane.
