Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺一個飛機的姿勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fly like a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把胳膊舉起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raise your arms up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺成一個三角形\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together like a triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供奉的姿勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Out like an offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺一個飛機的姿勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then you fly like a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's goin' on, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch it on that, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意是要推銷給孩子的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're trying to market this thing to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個太緊了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this too tight for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是什么測試\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the fuck kind of test was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么意思  -算了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What do you mean? - Forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么算了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Forget about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not feeling it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做出最終決定前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you want to talk about numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要先討論一下酬勞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before you make your final decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你應該會對酬勞有感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel like you're gonna feel these numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's this, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匿名條款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's this anonymity clause.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,標準保密條款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Standard nondisclosure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能說你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't say who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會說你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we don't say who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣能保護我們雙方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Protects us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會知道是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one'll know it's me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:15:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是信任問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's about trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他推銷這些玩具的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, um, everyone else who promotes these toys,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要簽一份這個嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they sign one of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他演員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The other actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么其他演員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What other actors?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you said this was gonna be huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美翻了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tested through the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是圣誕大促銷吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a Santa' n' the all thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有幾個迷怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many other Pookas are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾遜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilson,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is all you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個迷怪  一個你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One Pooka, one you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一個夢想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司絕對會愛上你  所以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Corporate is gonna love you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}get comfortable,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就回去好好休息  給\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}take the rest of the day off. Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都沒有丟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And nothing's missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都沒有嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}nothing at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他們是怎么進來的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you have an idea how they got in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門上著鎖  窗戶關著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The door was locked, the windows were closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你  親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm telling you, darling,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該報警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you should call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有東西被偷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多破碎的東西是無法彌補的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot was broken that you can't un-break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.91,0:19:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樓里以前發生過這種事嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has this ever happened in this building before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我印象里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First time I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個安靜的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a rather quiet place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天去找個鄰居\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll borrow a vacuum tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借一個吸塵器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from one of the neighbors
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理掉被我們遺漏的玻璃碎渣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for any bits of glass that we've missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在房間里就穿著鞋子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meanwhile, you keep your shoes on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松點  親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Relax, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有人闖入很可怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, break-ins can be scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你在自己的家里感到害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They make you feel scared in your own home,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒人會回來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but no one is coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}迷怪來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:21:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  威爾遜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's beautiful, Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就算我不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That way you won't feel alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不會感到孤單了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even when I'm not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我要去工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, off to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的新工作是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this new job?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都沒怎么和我提過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've hardly told me anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是得穿著頭套的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, it's just this thing in a costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我  沒什么意思的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trust me, there's nothing interesting about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}迷怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}調皮還是乖巧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}你永遠不知道迷怪會怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}警告  非常好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.78,0:22:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣誕老人列了一張單子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's making a list,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.97,0:22:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}迷怪  圣誕節的新寵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反復核查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's checking it twice,
