Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.75,0:25:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下了我一跳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.35,0:26:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.37,0:26:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是威爾遜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.57,0:26:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅拉尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.62,0:26:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到你很高興\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a pleasure to meet you.
