Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.29,0:26:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will be the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.32,0:26:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幢房是1966年建成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The house was built in '66.
