Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.73,0:42:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去燒水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll put the kettle on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.65,0:42:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽經常說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.61,0:42:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什么事是一壺好茶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that a good cuppa can't fix,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.49,0:42:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決不了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as my mum used to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.66,0:42:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這當然是個謊言了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, that's a lie, though, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.74,0:42:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的謊言反而能幫助你度過一些難關  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some lies help you get through things, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.96,0:42:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她就是靠濃茶安穩度過了閃電戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good, strong tea got her through the Blitz, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.46,0:42:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我有點問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think there's something wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.01,0:42:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都有問題  親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's something wrong with all of us, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.31,0:42:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  雷德  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Red, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.89,0:42:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的記憶出現空白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm losing time, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.98,0:42:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失控了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm losing control.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.57,0:43:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Things are all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.24,0:43:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.49,0:43:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have this job,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.49,0:43:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇見一個女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and this girl, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.33,0:43:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.04,0:43:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.34,0:43:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這個東西  這...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But then, there's this-- this thing, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.84,0:43:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個東西...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this other thing, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.39,0:43:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.01,0:43:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我記起為什么搬過來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel like I remember why I moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.35,0:43:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了逃離\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I could get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.61,0:43:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃離...痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Away...from pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.07,0:43:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃離給人造成痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Away from causing pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.29,0:43:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有后悔的事  親愛的威爾遜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone has regrets, Wilson darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.75,0:44:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生活很艱難\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Life is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.13,0:44:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都會犯錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.13,0:44:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起做出正確的決定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make good choices now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.89,0:44:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.20,0:44:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.50,0:44:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊  來啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.25,0:44:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good, aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.17,0:44:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊  伙計們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.29,0:44:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷怪  來啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Pooka, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.76,0:44:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.14,0:44:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天玩的開心嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So did you have fun today?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.43,0:45:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what you're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.81,0:45:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What am I up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.52,0:45:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想討好我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trying to get on my good side
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.98,0:45:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我媽媽更喜歡你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that my mom will like you more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.11,0:45:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用給我買禮物或者給我們買圣誕樹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to buy me things or get us a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.70,0:45:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要陪著我們  對我們好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just have to stick around and be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.74,0:45:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.70,0:45:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡圣誕節嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't like Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.50,0:45:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說很復雜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tricky time for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.54,0:45:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我能讓泰再愛上圣誕節\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I can make Ty love Christmas again,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.00,0:45:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那周末我要給他辦個小圣誕派對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I'm throwing him a little Christmas party at the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.09,0:45:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫很多他的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get a lot of his friends together,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.13,0:45:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放音樂啊  交換禮物啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}play some music, exchange gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.89,0:45:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So your mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.43,0:45:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和我說了你們下周要辦個圣誕派對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she told me about your Christmas party next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.22,0:45:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你高興嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you, uh, excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.77,0:45:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  肯定會和迷怪一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. It's gonna be a Pooka thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.64,0:45:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多棒啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How cool is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.94,0:45:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, tell me this, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.15,0:45:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想見見真正的迷怪嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}would you like to meet Pooka for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.03,0:45:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-靠  當然了  -我聽到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hell yes! - I heard that!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.74,0:45:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這棵了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.33,0:45:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這棵嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.91,0:46:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  就是這棵了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, this is the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.21,0:46:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.30,0:46:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來看看這棵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come and have a look at this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.18,0:46:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.80,0:46:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能幫我們拍一張照嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you mind taking our picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.43,0:46:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, of course, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.93,0:46:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.81,0:46:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.32,0:46:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這璀璨的燈光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at all the pretty lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.36,0:46:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會傷害我媽媽嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you going to hurt my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.20,0:46:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會傷害我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you going to hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.25,0:46:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅拉尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Melanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.30,0:48:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}迷怪
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.42,0:48:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用跟他保證的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, you didn't have to promise that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.75,0:48:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一整個早上都在和朋友們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's been telling all his friends all morning
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.84,0:48:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吹噓那東西會來參加他的派對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that that thing is coming to his party.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.84,0:49:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是好意  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you meant well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.30,0:49:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候如果沒有來的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's going to be really embarrassed
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.43,0:49:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會感覺很丟臉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when it doesn't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.93,0:49:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么會沒有來呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why wouldn't it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.81,0:49:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-拜托  -不  我和你說了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. - No, I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.60,0:49:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.44,0:49:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你說了  你為什么不相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you, why-- why wouldn't you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.11,0:49:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你  只是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I trust you, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.98,0:49:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.07,0:49:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用為了我而承諾太多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to overpromise to impress me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.82,0:49:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.37,0:49:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想要給他空歡喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not trying to put things in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.17,0:49:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎  絕對會來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? It's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.30,0:49:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.34,0:50:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.38,0:50:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  迷怪來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mom, Pooka's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.65,0:50:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢信嗎  他在我家呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you believe he's here at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.70,0:50:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.16,0:50:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.16,0:50:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得還行吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, it's okay, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.41,0:50:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你跟他說過話嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you--have you gotten to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.29,0:50:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是給小孩玩的  有什么大不了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's for little kids, what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.00,0:51:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸不在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your dad isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.92,0:51:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.38,0:51:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就...誰都知道你爸爸的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just--everybody knows about your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.15,0:51:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.24,0:51:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.58,0:51:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很能理解發生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really don't understand what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.62,0:51:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.04,0:51:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也不說什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not saying much either.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.88,0:51:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You okay, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.89,0:51:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我今天沒有來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I wasn't able to make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.39,0:51:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.68,0:51:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我習慣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.52,0:52:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能告訴我發生了什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you tell me what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.23,0:52:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾遜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.61,0:52:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了他做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.53,0:52:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm pretty sure I know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.04,0:52:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的太害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was really scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.46,0:52:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們嚇壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're livid.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.30,0:52:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該過來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.80,0:52:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真希望你當時能在場  -我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I wish you had been. - I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.05,0:52:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that it went so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.02,0:52:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都希望泰能覺得那個派對很特別\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We both wanted the party to be special for Ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.14,0:52:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是誰啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who was that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.11,0:52:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -穿那身衣服的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - That guy in the costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.11,0:52:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不明白怎么會讓這種家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just don't understand how someone like that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.32,0:52:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-跟小孩一起  -你是在怪我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- could be around kids. - Are you blaming me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.28,0:52:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是不明白怎么會發生這種事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I just don't understand what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.45,0:52:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.20,0:53:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾遜  你看上去非常冷淡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilson, you just seem kind of passive,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.71,0:53:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時真的很可怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it was really awful,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.54,0:53:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不明白  好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I just don't understand, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.84,0:53:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們很喜歡那個玩具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The kids love that toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.17,0:53:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是以為請那個玩偶來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just thought that having the character there
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.97,0:53:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孩子們互動會非常特別\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}interacting with them, that it would be special.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.64,0:53:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我明白  -我只想為泰做一些好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I get that. - I just wanted to do something nice for Ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.93,0:53:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道會發生這種事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How was I supposed to know something like that would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.10,0:53:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不是那個意思  -我只是想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's not what I meant. - I just wanted to do
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.27,0:53:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你和泰做一些好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something nice for you and Ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.86,0:53:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想那樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.96,0:53:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.30,0:53:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.01,0:53:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那棵樹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.68,0:53:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么樹  -上帝啊  梅拉尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What tree? - Christ, Melanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.22,0:53:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不喜歡那棵該死的樹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you didn't like the goddamned tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.43,0:54:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以直接告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you could have just told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.22,0:54:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣跟我說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't talk to me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.48,0:54:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你到底怎么回事  -我感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What has gotten into you? - I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.10,0:54:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是信任問題  我感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like it's about trust, I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.15,0:54:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不信任我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you don't trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.73,0:54:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有告訴我真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.15,0:54:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我沒有告訴你什么的真相  -一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What don't I tell you the truth about? - Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.82,0:54:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于那棵樹  泰的爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About the tree, Ty's dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.11,0:54:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和這一切有什么關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What does he have to do with any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.53,0:54:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還在你們生活中嗎[照片上]\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is he still in the picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.62,0:54:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是泰的爸爸  他不在我們生活中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he's Ty's dad, he's not in the picture
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.66,0:54:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他在照片上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he's in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.54,0:54:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣  沒有那么簡單\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the way it works, it's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.67,0:54:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  人人都知道泰的爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, everybody knows about Ty's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.05,0:54:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我之外人人都知道他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody knows about him but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.01,0:54:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你馬上離開這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.10,0:54:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.69,0:54:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.11,0:54:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.15,0:54:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.03,0:55:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}迷怪
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.63,0:56:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}迷怪故障導致大范圍回收
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.73,0:56:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本季度最熱的玩具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The hottest toy of the season
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.06,0:56:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶來了最深的失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has turned into its biggest disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.69,0:56:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉磯各地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Countless malfunctioning Pookas
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.14,0:56:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.32,0:56:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返廠了無數出故障的迷怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have been returned throughout Los Angeles,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.56,0:56:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}垃圾\N去他媽的迷怪
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.53,0:56:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母們抱怨原先大熱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with parents complaining that the popular
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.61,0:56:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"調皮或乖巧"的玩具突然壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Naughty or Nice" toys are suddenly broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.73,0:56:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}最大的失望
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.45,0:56:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們全都只會用奇怪的聲音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all of them saying nothing but
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.74,0:56:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重復一段原先錄好的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one bizarre prerecorded phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.24,0:56:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這璀璨的燈光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at all the pretty lights,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.16,0:56:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這璀璨的燈光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at all the pretty lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.75,0:56:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生  你覺得迷怪怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, how do you feel about Pooka?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.37,0:56:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是一個廢物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a total rip-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.21,0:56:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日夜夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All day, all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.29,0:56:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會重復\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it just kept saying the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.75,0:56:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.09,0:56:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我退回了我的錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I-- I got my money back,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.93,0:56:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我浪費的時間呢  這簡直是胡扯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but where's my time? This is bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.80,0:56:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒錯  -這簡直是胡扯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah! - This is bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.26,0:56:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的時間呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is my time?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.71,0:56:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要我們的錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want our money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.83,0:56:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}迷怪中心  停止營業
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.54,0:56:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}迷怪中心  停止營業\N直到有新的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.87,0:57:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.38,0:57:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你把這個帶過來  非常感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for bringing this by, appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.18,0:57:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs18\b1}迷怪\N調皮還是乖巧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.13,0:57:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去不大好  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't look so good, man, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.47,0:57:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和你談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.01,0:57:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得公司搞錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, I think corporate has got it wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.14,0:57:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得繼續下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we just need to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.22,0:57:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什么  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you talking about, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.35,0:57:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都回收了  公關危機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's been a recall, the PR's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.35,0:57:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經回不去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no coming back from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.23,0:57:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能讓幾個小小的意外毀了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't just let a few fucking incidents ruin everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.69,0:57:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不僅僅只是幾個小意外  威爾遜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's more than a few incidents, Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.62,0:57:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些玩具完蛋呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The toys are busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.49,0:57:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有人想買了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody wants to buy them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.95,0:57:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  還好你把這些帶過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, I'm glad you brought this,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.16,0:57:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我可得拿回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'cause I gotta take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.62,0:57:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.04,0:57:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's going on, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.79,0:57:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不屬于你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This doesn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.96,0:57:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.67,0:58:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.09,0:58:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息休息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take some time for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.51,0:58:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出城玩玩什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out of town or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.77,0:58:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過好你的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go live life.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.39,0:58:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找兄弟們喝幾杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go have some beers with your bros.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.35,0:58:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須穿上這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to be inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.07,0:58:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得控制你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gotta get a grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.12,0:58:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受一切的結束  伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay for this to be over, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.07,0:59:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來煩我  走開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave me alone, just go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.16,0:59:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅  拜托  我需要解釋一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mel, please, I need to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.16,0:59:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mel?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.83,0:59:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mel?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.96,0:59:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mel?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.91,1:00:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和你談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.04,1:00:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, love.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.21,1:00:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊  雷德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus Christ. Red.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.00,1:00:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉  親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, love.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.13,1:00:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.31,1:00:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該離開了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time for you to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.64,1:03:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是梅拉尼  請留言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi, it's Melanie, leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.68,1:03:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅拉尼  是我  威爾遜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi, Melani, it's me, Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.56,1:03:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽我說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.65,1:03:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I miss you, and, 
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.49,1:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I understand, um,
